&lt;templatestyles src="Reflist/styles.css" /&gt;

</doc>
<doc id="568898" url="https://ml.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=568898" title="United Nations Declaration on the Rights of Peasants">
United Nations Declaration on the Rights of Peasants



